{"analytics_identifier":"D102","base_path":"/government/organisations/food-standards-agency","content_id":"447f8075-1c8c-40d3-8119-3e45ea9e6496","description":"The Food Standards Agency (FSA) is responsible for food safety and food hygiene in England, Wales and Northern Ireland. It works with local authorities to enforce food safety regulations and its staff work in meat plants to check the standards are being met. The FSA also has responsibility for labelling policy in Wales and Northern Ireland, and for nutrition policy in Northern Ireland. FSA is a non-ministerial department, supported by 2 agencies and public bodies .","details":{"acronym":"FSA","alternative_format_contact_email":"fsa.communications@food.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Food Standards Agency (FSA) is responsible for food safety and food hygiene in England, Wales and Northern Ireland. It works with local authorities to enforce food safety regulations and its staff work in meat plants to check the standards are being met.</p>\n\n<p>The FSA also has responsibility for labelling policy in Wales and Northern Ireland, and for nutrition policy in Northern Ireland.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Food Standards Agency\">FSA</abbr> is a non-ministerial department, supported by <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations#food-standards-agency\">2 agencies and public bodies</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-of-health","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"Food Standards Agency"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/food-standards-agency/about/accessible-documents-policy","title":"Accessible documents policy"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"http://www.food.gov.uk/"},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"non_ministerial_department","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/FoodStandardsAgency","service_type":"facebook","title":"Food Standards Agency"},{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/company/food-standards-agency/","service_type":"linkedin","title":"Food Standards Agency"},{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/user/FoodStandardsAgency","service_type":"youtube","title":"Food Standards Agency"},{"href":"https://www.instagram.com/foodgov/","service_type":"instagram","title":"Food Standards Agency"}]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-01-11T14:16:59+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D102","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/food-standards-agency","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/food-standards-agency","base_path":"/government/organisations/food-standards-agency","content_id":"447f8075-1c8c-40d3-8119-3e45ea9e6496","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-05-11T09:09:52Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Food Standards Agency","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/food-standards-agency","withdrawn":false}],"mainstream_browse_pages":[{"api_path":"/api/content/browse/business/food-hospitality-retail","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/browse/business/food-hospitality-retail","base_path":"/browse/business/food-hospitality-retail","content_id":"b02faf6d-1044-4dc8-9553-892b0c273f65","description":"Start and run your restaurant, café, pub, shop or food business ","document_type":"mainstream_browse_page","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-23T10:27:31Z","schema_name":"mainstream_browse_page","title":"Food, hospitality and retail","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/food-hospitality-retail","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/ian-young","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/ian-young","base_path":"/government/people/ian-young","content_id":"a8780cc4-d8ba-483e-b069-521695f7acb2","details":{"image":{"url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69de170b8e256133a84224f1/s465_Professor_Ian_Young.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"27f99441-323e-484c-a603-2c0228b4502b","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2026-03-16T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8477fdf1-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Scientific Adviser is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the integrity of the processes used to source scientific evidence and ensure expert scientific advice is available to the agency</li>\n  <li>representing the agency in the community of departmental Chief Scientific Advisers and the wider scientific community</li>\n  <li>championing science within the agency through developing its scientists’ expertise</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The CSA has overall responsibility for all of the analytical disciplines from which the agency draws advice: natural and physical sciences, social science, economics, operational research and statistics.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"chief_scientific_advisor_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-22T10:06:31Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Food Standards Agency Chief Scientific Adviser","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T10:30:16Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Professor Ian Young - FSA Chief Scientific Adviser","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T10:29:30Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Professor Ian Young","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/ian-young","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/susan-jebb","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/susan-jebb","base_path":"/government/people/susan-jebb","content_id":"d33356ac-b2bf-430d-801f-a926ab2d53f4","details":{"image":{"url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ca593c2c5db1b1db67e905/s465_Professor_Susan_Jebb_2.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"46ff5c7a-6b4d-4056-b3d4-2e9e1ae60d7b","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2021-06-14T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"91da74ad-4cba-4d50-b25b-f58e16256d77","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T14:38:13Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chair of the Food Standards Agency","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T14:40:20Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Professor Susan Jebb OBE, PhD, FRCP (Hon), FMedSci - Chair of the Food Standards Agency","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-28T07:08:49Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Professor Susan Jebb OBE, PhD, FRCP (Hon), FMedSci","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/susan-jebb","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/rhian-hayward","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/rhian-hayward","base_path":"/government/people/rhian-hayward","content_id":"9948787d-3ea7-426d-b7d7-394b1c48d29f","details":{"image":{"url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685d5770f85b4b993fd752eb/s465_Dr_Rhian_Hayward.JPG"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"3458cc9e-c8b7-4b2b-acf7-f036f0828413","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2023-09-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"f2edb1bc-43a8-4a52-b188-8c726a68abc4","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T15:13:41Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Food Standards Agency Board Member","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T15:11:00Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Dr Rhian Hayward MBE - Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"b95a1d96-aed4-4e49-80d0-dd2d58ce32ec","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2025-02-01T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"822769b6-1c7e-42da-8163-7ce6f43f66b9","details":{"body":"<p>As a member of the Wales Office Departmental Board, Audit and Risk Assurance Committee (ARAC) and Outcome Delivery Plan (ODP) Implementation Committee, the Non-Executive Director supports the Lead Non-Executive in ensuring the effective and successful governance of the Department by:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensuring the Departmental Board and ARAC define the vision, values, culture and strategy of the organisation and set a high standard for ethics and responsible conduct of public business.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring the Departmental Board and ARAC maintain appropriate governance and internal controls, including ensuring sound financial, risk and performance management regimes are in place and the Department has the capacity to deliver.</li>\n  <li>Actively challenging the Board on key issues including the Business Plan and Strategic Risks.</li>\n  <li>Monitoring the delivery of the Department’s ODP through being a member of the ODP Implementation Committee.</li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Ensuring the Department’s Senior Management Team is subjected to constructive challenge in respect of the performance of the organisation; and</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>Providing counsel, advice, and support to the Secretary of State for Wales and the executive team, acting as a sounding board and “critical friend” where necessary.</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-02-05T17:02:32Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director for the Wales Office","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-02-05T16:39:03Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Dr Rhian Hayward MBE - Non-Executive Director for the Wales Office","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-22T10:50:09Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Dr Rhian Hayward MBE","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/rhian-hayward","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/timothy-riley","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/timothy-riley","base_path":"/government/people/timothy-riley","content_id":"f4356a76-23d7-4a9c-ad00-57767be2653a","details":{"image":{"url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69de60f22b60817d99ff8e53/s465_Timothy_Riley.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"3a234731-2289-42bc-9a58-c0a4f7aeb2d3","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2024-01-01T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"ee8aca3a-9a8f-427f-bdb1-d8b77b40e08e","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T15:19:33Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Chair of the Food Standards Agency","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T15:19:00Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Timothy Riley - Food Standards Agency Board Member","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-04-22T10:51:14Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Dr Timothy Riley","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/timothy-riley","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/frank-atherton","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/pe